1}, {\"ngram\": \"his first-round singles\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-time major winner, famously known as the King of Clay,faces Hungary's Marton Fucsovicsin his opening singles match and is projected to play his rivalNovak Djokovicin a blockbuster second-round showdown at Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.998893793584032, \"rank\": 0.0011056973880467396, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.8493083334441812, \"rank\": 0.09385219097447657, \"text\": \"Marton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marton,_New_Zealand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 22-time major winner\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the King\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"Clay\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"his opening singles match\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivalNovak\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"Djokovicin\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"a blockbuster second-round showdown\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland-Garros\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, playing his last Olympics, has also formed a Spanish dream team with Wimbledon championCarlos Alcarazand they are set to lock horns with Argentine duo Maximo Gonzalez and Andres Molteni in their first-round match.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"e